Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.74,0:02:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖母小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.79,0:02:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七十一話\N傀王的陰謀  翔伍誤入陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.44,0:03:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.41,0:03:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.72,0:03:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在哪裏 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我會在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.94,0:03:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,項鏈呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉到哪裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.86,0:03:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼渾身是傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.57,0:04:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種傷怎麼能說是沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖母小姐 我來遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.18,0:04:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼 離開她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.79,0:04:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莊三 別這樣\N這個人已經受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.69,0:04:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能見死不救\N放心 你退下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.74,0:04:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.44,0:04:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別動 忍耐點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的行為跟你長相不符\N一點也不溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.61,0:04:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因為我面對的是\N像你這樣的粗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,粗人 什麼粗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是有名有姓的\N我叫做相樂左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.12,0:04:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相樂左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.79,0:05:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 你少給我隨便下定義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又不瞭解我什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.16,0:05:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.57,0:05:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是每天跟人吵架\N吃飯都是用賒帳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.57,0:05:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還整天睡在別人家裏\N無所事事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說中了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.51,0:05:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏也有傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.45,0:05:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖母小姐…你的名字很怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.79,0:05:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是綽號吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.09,0:05:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒禮貌 那是洗禮的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.13,0:05:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…你的本名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.40,0:05:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒必要告訴你\N能夠叫我那名字的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.20,0:05:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上只有一個\N我哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.54,0:05:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 那你哥應該引以為榮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.35,0:05:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過…你為什麼…\N要對我這麼親切呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腳放在那上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.59,0:06:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你別誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.16,0:06:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是在完成我的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到有人受傷而不救助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,違反神的教導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神的教導？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.91,0:06:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神希望人有關懷之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.84,0:06:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不懂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.31,0:06:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的搞不懂\N你的言行跟你口中的神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.68,0:06:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的大哥是天草翔伍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.72,0:06:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是想掌控\N這個國家的大壞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.22,0:06:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你真的以關懷之心為重\N為什麼不阻止你大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.93,0:06:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥做的事絕對不會錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.90,0:06:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥…\N他一人背負了許多人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.37,0:06:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是想要救人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.57,0:07:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他抱持著你絕對沒辦法理解\N的崇高的理想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把人命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.45,0:07:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把人命踐踏在腳底\N哪裏是崇高了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.99,0:07:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我絕不原諒天草翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.69,0:07:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是專程來打倒哥哥的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.46,0:07:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在京都殺死三個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.70,0:07:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了你們那崇高的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.74,0:07:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天草翔伍踐踏人命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.41,0:07:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥…哥哥絕沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.75,0:07:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把項鏈還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.69,0:07:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還給我 那是我的寶物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.26,0:07:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,項鏈是媽媽的遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.43,0:07:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…已經不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你丟掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.77,0:07:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.44,0:08:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖母小姐 聖母小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.98,0:08:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不原諒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.55,0:08:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以哥哥的名字下令\N禁止你離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.62,0:08:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖媽小姐 聖媽小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.46,0:08:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對啦 小雪 是聖母啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.16,0:08:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖母小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.80,0:08:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 今天來預習注音\N然後聽神的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒 神的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.61,0:08:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖母小姐 神真的存在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.38,0:08:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為…我爸爸相信神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.01,0:08:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻被殺死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.28,0:08:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他又沒有做壞事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.19,0:08:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是 找到項鏈的時候\N被打的好慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.46,0:08:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.69,0:09:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神愛世人 很快的\N會來救大家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.53,0:09:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 翔伍大人不是說\N要建造幸福的國家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.30,0:09:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔伍大人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.87,0:09:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家來祈禱吧\N這樣就不會再痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.77,0:09:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不用流淚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.31,0:09:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓大家可以輕鬆活下去的\N夢幻般的國度在接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.25,0:09:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情進展完全在預料中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.99,0:09:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些國家\N想把日本變為殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.13,0:09:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名叫天草翔伍的不世英雄\N在日本製造內亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.30,0:09:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對他們而言這也是最佳機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.90,0:09:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要可以減弱明治政府實力\N他們願意給予全面支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.74,0:09:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.64,0:09:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最先進的槍支、大炮\N如果還需要其它東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,50艘戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.05,0:09:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.12,0:09:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還要一萬名士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.52,0:10:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於救世主的出現\N信徒們一直在增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以神子\N天草翔伍的名字為號召
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.03,0:10:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一年內光是島原地方\N都可能聚集好幾萬民眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…我去交涉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.24,0:10:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著\N我們要建築的是神的國度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.44,0:10:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是西方的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.44,0:10:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同意跟外國勢力聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.11,0:10:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為我把他們當做是\N信奉同一個神的同胞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.75,0:10:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到50艘戰艦跟\N一萬名士兵的援助的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會危及我的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.62,0:10:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟他們締結契約吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.59,0:10:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不許殖民地化 一定要\N他們保證神之國的絕對獨立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是被拒絕呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.57,0:10:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫無理想地建國\N無任何意義可言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.14,0:10:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事不再考慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.71,0:11:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.51,0:11:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的大哥賤踏人命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.06,0:12:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無意跟你吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.93,0:12:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會忘記你的好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.80,0:12:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有拋棄那個項鏈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.87,0:12:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的寶物\N我無論如何一定找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.51,0:12:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請務必相信我 等待我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.35,0:12:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助那傢伙到底去哪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.61,0:13:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你睡著了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.32,0:13:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我只是在聽風的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失明以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.39,0:13:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去眼睛健在時\N所看不到的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.76,0:14:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得好像變得可以看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.80,0:14:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是若是一直失明下去\N你怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.50,0:14:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最終應該是我超越他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.04,0:14:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,互相使出秘技天翔龍閃\N打敗天草翔伍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.38,0:14:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除此之外沒別的可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.26,0:14:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨夜交過手之後\N我的信念更堅強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.63,0:14:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果天草翔伍是個靈魂腐敗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.67,0:14:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的飛天御劍流的劍招\N絕不可能那樣運用自如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.04,0:14:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必需\N再跟天草翔伍交手一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的身體…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我失明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.79,0:15:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在是什麼樣的表情\N我想都不用想就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.23,0:15:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起這雙眼睛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.13,0:15:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你臉上失去笑容這件事\N更令我擔心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.28,0:15:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.71,0:15:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的外褲干了 我幫你縫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是小操嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.89,0:15:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 聽說你眼睛失明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.27,0:15:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.37,0:15:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊的 別這樣搖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.71,0:15:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.78,0:15:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有得到什麼線索了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 那個那個 沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.08,0:16:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬無一失 我得到天草翔伍\N跟他妹倆人最大的秘密了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.00,0:16:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這東西怎麼在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.14,0:16:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是荷蘭領事館的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.75,0:16:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.65,0:16:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這裏偷偷摸摸幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在查什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.83,0:16:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒時間跟你玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點急事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是那個絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.24,0:17:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火龍 以風壓斬斷空氣\N是世上只有我會使用的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.32,0:17:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個人很囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.72,0:17:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.82,0:17:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來試試火龍這招術\N是否世上真的只有你會使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.91,0:17:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火龍…這招我好像也會嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分出勝負了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.93,0:17:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到別人使出自己的絕招\N使你忘我了是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.80,0:18:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 鬧得有點過火了\N傷口竟然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.84,0:18:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了\N你現在下手我就無法反抗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.78,0:18:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再壞的壞蛋也要施予同情\N這是聖母小姐的教導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.95,0:18:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我不願承認\N但…你的拳頭威力十足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有翔伍大人\N可以掌管生殺大權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.80,0:18:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是神 我怕殺人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.27,0:18:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我發過誓\N要服侍翔伍與聖母小姐到死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.44,0:18:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是小時候的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.09,0:19:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她花了兩個月時間照顧我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.83,0:19:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我頭一次遇見\N沒把我當垃圾對待的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.60,0:19:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不對 他們倆\N成為我心目中的神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.74,0:19:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了他們\N我隨時都可以拋棄性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.12,0:19:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 天草大人太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.12,0:20:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他以為沒有外國勢力介入\N在日本的內亂可以成功？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.79,0:20:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光靠口頭說說\N是無法推翻明治政府的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.13,0:20:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把事情推動到這裏的我\N又有什麼立場可言了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.67,0:20:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心 照我說的做就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.67,0:20:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.41,0:20:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天草翔伍 他的魅力確實強大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.25,0:20:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像個神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.42,0:20:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是老實說 我不是被神\N而是被惡魔給吸引了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真是熱血沸騰呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.43,0:20:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去年在大陸街頭\N首次遇到天草翔伍時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.23,0:20:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很確信一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.87,0:20:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的多年的計劃將要推動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.74,0:20:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 我得到\N天草翔伍這根魔法棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.98,0:21:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光是揮個手\N信徒們就像螞蟻一樣群聚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.58,0:21:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓螞蟻們不要命地戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.09,0:21:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是足以破壞這個國家的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.56,0:21:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之那個男人是徹頭徹尾\N值得寶貝的魔法棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.87,0:21:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山東先生\N我找到有趣的東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.81,0:21:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.67,0:21:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.54,0:21:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是聖母小姐的項鏈呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.84,0:21:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來到這裏的途中撿到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.21,0:22:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相樂左之助\N是不該再見面的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不畏神的罪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.58,0:22:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還想打倒大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.92,0:22:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣…為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.25,0:22:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我還…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.19,0:22:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天草翔伍\N與聖母小姐的秘密？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.00,0:22:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.36,0:22:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,島原發生的悲劇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.40,0:22:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密就隱藏在那之中

